      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream! This car has been pampered since day one\u2014always garage-kept, meticulously cleaned, and there isn't a single scratch or dent to be found. It still has that wonderful new-car smell! I've taken such good care of it, and I know you're going to fall in love the moment you see it. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
