      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. This one-owner gem has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, preserving the deep luster of its original factory paint, which remains entirely free of swirls, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather seats are supple with no bolster wear, and the dashboard remains pristine under UV protection. Mechanically, the car is flawless, benefiting from a documented history of preventative maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. Every button, switch, and feature operates with precision. This is a rare opportunity to own a preserved piece of automotive history that requires absolutely nothing but a new home.",
